  "content": "<p data-pid=\"m9rhkB-t\">推荐一波 Anki：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8591356d2fc3abfbeadd3889b0cea26_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"452\" data-original-token=\"v2-e8591356d2fc3abfbeadd3889b0cea26\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e8591356d2fc3abfbeadd3889b0cea26_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1440&#39; height=&#39;452&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"452\" data-original-token=\"v2-e8591356d2fc3abfbeadd3889b0cea26\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e8591356d2fc3abfbeadd3889b0cea26_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e8591356d2fc3abfbeadd3889b0cea26_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b6bd20c00a3d181d977f5b0f1058d0fb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1120\" data-original-token=\"v2-b6bd20c00a3d181d977f5b0f1058d0fb\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b6bd20c00a3d181d977f5b0f1058d0fb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1440&#39; height=&#39;1120&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"1120\" data-original-token=\"v2-b6bd20c00a3d181d977f5b0f1058d0fb\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b6bd20c00a3d181d977f5b0f1058d0fb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b6bd20c00a3d181d977f5b0f1058d0fb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6af28f9fa600e0f19287b164cd2c60dc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"587\" data-rawheight=\"396\" data-original-token=\"v2-6af28f9fa600e0f19287b164cd2c60dc\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"587\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-6af28f9fa600e0f19287b164cd2c60dc_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;587&#39; height=&#39;396&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"587\" data-rawheight=\"396\" data-original-token=\"v2-6af28f9fa600e0f19287b164cd2c60dc\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"587\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-6af28f9fa600e0f19287b164cd2c60dc_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6af28f9fa600e0f19287b164cd2c60dc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"evj3ciGT\">高中化学的知识点非常多，想要完全掌握它们并在高考前保持熟练，科学地规划复习是十分重要的。</p><p data-pid=\"fEKKxuPh\">Anki 是一款能够根据学生复习反馈调整复习安排的笔记软件。在 Anki 中我们可以将平时的笔记、错题制作成复习卡片</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c94e6a7c90d78b044c678947c8fc2499_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-c94e6a7c90d78b044c678947c8fc2499\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c94e6a7c90d78b044c678947c8fc2499_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-c94e6a7c90d78b044c678947c8fc2499\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c94e6a7c90d78b044c678947c8fc2499_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c94e6a7c90d78b044c678947c8fc2499_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"xQ6gI69i\">然后每天 Anki 就会安排复习：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-051fdd4550216a841d8783c48cc3d531_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2340\" data-original-token=\"v2-051fdd4550216a841d8783c48cc3d531\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-051fdd4550216a841d8783c48cc3d531_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2340&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2340\" data-original-token=\"v2-051fdd4550216a841d8783c48cc3d531\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-051fdd4550216a841d8783c48cc3d531_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-051fdd4550216a841d8783c48cc3d531_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Loke8ULX\">每天的复习都会整理成统计数据：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d577cc698753c351ade712d21157ecc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"711\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-original-token=\"v2-ed0c89733cf23af99a1ac094328c337c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3d4214322f07507d317881f60e2455b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"711\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5d577cc698753c351ade712d21157ecc_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;711&#39; height=&#39;1920&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"711\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-original-token=\"v2-ed0c89733cf23af99a1ac094328c337c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3d4214322f07507d317881f60e2455b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"711\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5d577cc698753c351ade712d21157ecc_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5d577cc698753c351ade712d21157ecc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"hB8KxgOc\">Anki 支持 windows(免费)、mac(免费)、linux(免费)、安卓(免费)、苹果(163元买断)等常见设备，并且可以多端同步，走到哪学到哪。</p><p data-pid=\"-lfU1FKp\">为了帮助高中生入门 Anki，我写了一份快速上手教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-acfa8f607f2d3c74ba5c660c3ab25df0_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1161\" data-image-height=\"500\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：Anki 教程(电子书)与 B 站 Ankidroid 教程(视频)快速通道</a><p data-pid=\"1Qp2jgC6\">希望对题主有所帮助。</p>",
